<h2 id="comments">Comments</h2>

<div id="c1">
<p>&#8220;Because I am a sad and lonely masochist&#8221;</p>

<p>Why all the self-loathing?</p>

<p>You got into a pretty good school yourself, you&#8217;ve been featured in Wired magazine, and Graham himself invited you to apply for YC&#8217;s first funding round (which, unlike the rest of us unknowns, guaranteed that you&#8217;d be accepted).</p>

<p>So why the long face?</p>

<p>Is it because you&#8217;re not physically imposing?</p>

<p>Are you worried your time at reddit/infogami won&#8217;t amount to anything?</p>

<p>Do you wish that Graham was a girl so you could make sweet love to him?</p>

<p>What is it?</p>

